org.daisy.streamline.api.config

Interface UserConfigurationsProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurationsProvider

    public interface UserConfigurationsProvider
extends ConfigurationsProvider
    Provides an interface for user configurations providers. A user configurations provider handles a set of configurations, each accessible via a configuration key. In addition, configurations can be added and removed.
